-300 according to Lucy.  I cast Lure of Ro (32 times in BoT east) stuck every time for full. Cast Tears of Arlyxir 26(26x3 because it hits for 3 tics) 78 times and was resisted 43 of the 78.  Both these spells have neg300 resistances check why does it not work? Anyone have any ideas? <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.swordoffate.com/images/sigs/Blitzkitty.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><br>
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=erumaroneverbright>Erumaron Everbright</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br>  Posts: 339<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/21/03 7:48 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Tears of Marr</span><hr size=1> there's a ~20% hard-coded resist rate but damn...that's like 50% that resisted for you.  wonder if they borked it at some point. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=aauminki>Aauminki</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Channeler</span><br>  Posts: 186<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/22/03 8:39 pm)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Tears of Marr</span><hr size=1> ToMarr is not lure, it's a regular cold resist rain (like ToPrexus).<br>
<br>
Tears of Arlyxir (the lure one) works fine. It <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>is</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> lure resist, as in you can cast it on mobs that you need (fire) lures to hit normally - however it still has the hardcoded rain resist rate of 20% which increases dramatically when the mob has 10% or lower hp left.<br>
<br>
Tears are much lower aggro than DDs, in fights where mana isn't an issue I usually chain two Tear (rain) spells, eg. Marr/Prexus on Fennin Ro. <p><big><center><b><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=370955 target=blank>Sage Aauminki Iceblade</a><br><a href=http://www.vazaelle.dk target=blank>Caer Cadarn</a></big><br>Vazaelle Server</center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=rombusmindspire>Rombus Mindspire</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><table width=111><tr><td style=filter:glow(color=#6633FF strength=1);font-family:arial;font-weight;bold;font-size:'1pt' nowrap><font size=1 color=#FFFFFF face=Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif>Forum Tyrant<br><br>Owned by Ikeya<BR>Destroying EverWars...<BR><a href=mailto:rombus@graffe.com style=text-decoration: none><u>Contact Rombus</u></font></td></tr></table></span><br>  Posts: 7350<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/23/03 8:39 am)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Tears of Marr</span><hr size=1> If you think tear / rain spells are useless and / or suck you should re-think your playstyle.  They own. <p><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.tritonguild.com/rombus/sig.gif"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="font-family:Verdana;font-size:xx-small;">Officer of Triton, Member of Team Ice, Povar<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->:. <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=458434" target="top">Rombus, Arcanist</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> .:. <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=5702" target="top">Rommy, Archon</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> .:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://makavelie.triton-teamice.com/" target="top">Always remember, never forget.</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=belarkan>Belarkan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br>  Posts: 397<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/23/03 8:49 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> re</span><hr size=1> I think most wizards see the red resist sentence displayed twice in a row as an afront (like i do), if all the resisted rains were doing like 20 dmg instead of 0, there would maybe less complains. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=yandidari>yandidari</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br>  Posts: 34<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/24/03 6:28 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Tears of Marr</span><hr size=1> i use tears or ro/marr alot in exp groups. i think its more mana efficent than dds and its less aggro, and something different to use. i used tears of ro on agnarr a couple times, forgot to take logs though, so i am not sure of the damage done or if it was better than draughts. i cant say that im happy with tears of arlyxir. i thought that it would hit 1 mob 4 times, but it doesnt, i get just as many resists from it as i do other rains, so since it does less damage i chose to stick with tears of ro. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=fqubedf3povar>FqubedF3povar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Channeler</span><br>  Posts: 211<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/24/03 1:18 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Tears of Marr</span><hr size=1> Normally ill cast a tear and chain in a draught, depending on how i think aggro is and mobs hps ill do it again or just med or DD, generally a 2 cycle is the most a mob sees on a normal exp group... and unless its a long fight thats the most your tanks can handle (without a single conc yet) before you get &quot;you will not evade me.....&quot;<br>
<br>
F3 <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showPrevMessage?topicID=934.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showNextMessage?topicID=934.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.emailToFriend?topicID=934.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.threadControl?topicID=934.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=934.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=934.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub140.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm60">Graffe Forum News<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm1">General EQ Discussion<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm5